{"title":"Esker Cycles Smokey Ti Hardtail","link":"https://theradavist.com/esker-cycles-smokey-ti-hardtail/","date":1718024433000,"content":"<p><em><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/search/Esker+Cycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Esker Cycles</a> is broadening its hardtail lineup with its most aggressive hardtail, the <a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/pages/smokey-ti?mc_cid=763d2bc3c8&amp;mc_eid=41d9857d47\" target=\"_blank\">Smokey Ti</a>. Let’s check it out…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"5352\" height=\"3568\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey-angle.jpg?fit=1200,3568&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey-angle.jpg?w=5352&amp;quality=75 5352w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey-angle.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey-angle.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey-angle.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey-angle.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey-angle.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Longer, lower, and slacker, the Smokey Ti has a 64.5º headtube angle and geometry optimized for a 160mm suspension fork. The frame has ample tire clearance, fitting up to a 2.6″ tire.</p>\n<p><em>Check out our <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/esker-cycles-hayduke-lvs-longtail-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Esker Hayduke LVS</a> and <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/esker-japhy-titanium-29er-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Japhy Ti review</a> for other titanium Esker chassis. </em></p>\n<p><img width=\"1066\" height=\"710\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey-Geo-Only.png?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey-Geo-Only.png?w=1066&amp;quality=75 1066w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey-Geo-Only.png?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w\" /> <img width=\"984\" height=\"1172\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey-Geo-and-Specs-.jpeg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey-Geo-and-Specs-.jpeg?w=984&amp;quality=75 984w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey-Geo-and-Specs-.jpeg?resize=768,915&amp;quality=75 768w\" /></p>\n<p>The Smokey Ti is constructed from seamless, butted, and cold-shaped 3/2.5 titanium, delivering a durable yet comfortable ride, and comes with Esker’s tried and true Portage Dropout System. Now updated with a Universal Derailleur Hanger (UDH). Portage Dropouts allow the frame to run with geared or singlespeed drivetrains and allow the rider to adjust chainstay length to fine tune the ride feel.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1366\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail5.jpg?fit=1200,1366&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail5.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail5.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail5.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail5.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail5.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1366\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail3.jpg?fit=1200,1366&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail3.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail3.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail3.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail3.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail3.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1366\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail2.jpg?fit=1200,1366&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail2.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail2.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail2.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail2.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/detail2.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Prioritizing durability and ease of maintenance, the Smokey Ti has external cable routing, a threaded bottom bracket, and a 44mm head tube. The Smokey boasts four different water bottle and accessory mounting positions, including a 3-pack mount on the downtube for when you need a little extra carrying capacity.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"5606\" height=\"3737\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey_frame.jpg?fit=1200,3737&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey_frame.jpg?w=5606&amp;quality=75 5606w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey_frame.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey_frame.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey_frame.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey_frame.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/06/Smokey_frame.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Frame Only: $2500</li>\n<li>Frame + Fork: Starting at $3100</li>\n<li>Complete Builds: Starting at $4500, with numerous upgrade options available.</li>\n<li>Complete Single Speed builds start at $4200</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/pages/smokey-ti?mc_cid=763d2bc3c8&amp;mc_eid=41d9857d47\" target=\"_blank\">Esker Cycles</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/esker-cycles-smokey-ti-hardtail/\">Esker Cycles Smokey Ti Hardtail</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"5664b2d12e20a6ed3f187983eff46620f158ff387e4f7d173be8ce848f26fd13","category":"Cycling"}